### ========================================
### WORKOUT EXERCISES - Relacionamento
### ========================================
### Rotas protegidas (requerem token JWT)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@token = seu-token-aqui

### Listar exercícios de um treino (substitua {workoutId} pelo ID real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Adicionar exercício ao treino (substitua {workoutId} e {exerciseId} pelos IDs reais)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "exercise_id": "{exerciseId}",
    "weight": 60.5,
    "sets": 3,
    "reps": 12
}

###

### Atualizar peso/séries/reps (substitua {workoutId} e {exerciseId} pelos IDs reais)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "weight": 65.0,
    "sets": 4,
    "reps": 10
}

###

### Atualizar apenas peso (atualização parcial)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "weight": 70.0
}

###

### Remover exercício do treino (substitua {workoutId} e {exerciseId} pelos IDs reais)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workouts/{workoutId}/exercises/{exerciseId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

